WEBVTT

01:34.560 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:38.320 --> 01:41.520
BEIYU NOSTALGIC NOODLES

02:01.440 --> 02:05.360
CHE YANQIN

02:15.560 --> 02:16.880
Hello, Aunt.

02:17.800 --> 02:18.880
Where are you?

02:23.600 --> 02:24.720
I'm reading a book.

02:24.800 --> 02:26.960
Hurry up and come back.
Pick me up some things on the way.

02:27.040 --> 02:28.280
We're waiting for them.

02:28.360 --> 02:29.800
- Got it.
- Hurry.

02:32.920 --> 02:34.880
Sorry, I have to leave now.

02:41.680 --> 02:42.720
Be careful on the road.

03:05.280 --> 03:06.880
WHEN YOU ARE OLD

04:13.720 --> 04:15.520
Why are you back so late?

04:15.600 --> 04:17.160
I studied somewhere.

04:18.200 --> 04:19.760
Here's the stuff you asked me to buy.

04:21.160 --> 04:23.200
What's there to study?

04:23.880 --> 04:25.800
I think you're just being lazy on purpose.

04:25.880 --> 04:28.480
There's a whole big family
waiting to eat at home.

04:28.560 --> 04:30.560
Couldn't you come back earlier to help?

04:31.080 --> 04:32.600
Honestly!

04:33.320 --> 04:35.640
This is the expensive
chicken soup I bought.

04:35.720 --> 04:37.280
You have to drink it all
to nourish yourself.

04:37.360 --> 04:39.760
I don't want that.
How can I finish all of it?

04:39.840 --> 04:40.960
Jiang, drink it.

04:41.040 --> 04:42.680
Why should she get
to drink such good stuff?

04:42.760 --> 04:44.280
She doesn't deserve it!

04:44.880 --> 04:48.000
Are you seducing
some new guy out there again?

04:48.520 --> 04:50.480
Listen, If you cause any more trouble,

04:50.560 --> 04:52.920
don't blame me for not
sparing your mom's face.

04:59.240 --> 05:01.240
Isn't it better to sit apart?

05:01.320 --> 05:02.760
You two can focus on your studies now.

05:02.840 --> 05:04.480
Worrying so much?

05:04.560 --> 05:05.720
You might lose your hair later.

05:07.360 --> 05:09.160
You keep coming here
to find me every weekend.

05:09.240 --> 05:10.280
Doesn't it affect your studies?

05:12.080 --> 05:13.120
What?

05:15.440 --> 05:17.400
I said, doesn't it affect your studies

05:17.480 --> 05:18.320
when you come to find me every weekend?

05:19.080 --> 05:20.120
Not at all.

05:20.200 --> 05:21.680
My grades are really good now.

05:22.280 --> 05:23.320
I've improved by leaps and bounds.

05:23.840 --> 05:25.160
I'm at the top of my class.

05:25.240 --> 05:26.320
I've made the honor roll.

05:29.800 --> 05:30.880
Sounds good.

05:39.360 --> 05:41.400
Last week, you left so urgently.

05:42.240 --> 05:43.280
Was something happening?

05:45.760 --> 05:46.840
I forgot.

05:50.480 --> 05:51.320
It's better that you forgot.

05:55.000 --> 05:57.320
By the way, I returned your book.
Did you get it?

06:13.760 --> 06:16.600
WHEN YOU ARE OLD

06:16.680 --> 06:20.440
I WON'T FORGET
THE TIME WE'VE SPENT TOGETHER

06:43.880 --> 06:45.600
3,122 DAYS

06:46.560 --> 06:49.840
DAY 60 OF LIVING TOGETHER OFFICIALLY

06:49.920 --> 06:52.040
Stay safe on your way!

06:52.120 --> 06:53.960
STAY SAFE

06:54.480 --> 06:55.480
Stay safe on your way!

06:55.560 --> 06:57.080
- Who are you?
- I'm accompanying her.

06:58.600 --> 06:59.720
Jiang.

07:00.800 --> 07:02.040
What are you doing here?

07:02.120 --> 07:03.200
I came to find you.

07:04.720 --> 07:05.560
If there's something, let's talk outside.

07:05.640 --> 07:06.880
- This is my workplace.
- No…

07:06.960 --> 07:08.440
Let's talk here.

07:09.680 --> 07:12.800
Jiang, you were upset
at our place last time.

07:12.880 --> 07:14.520
Was it because you saw Xin?

07:15.320 --> 07:17.080
Let me tell you, I've already talked
to your mom about this.

07:17.160 --> 07:18.360
I said there's no need
to hide it from you.

07:18.440 --> 07:20.560
I told her that you are a reasonable girl

07:20.640 --> 07:22.200
and wouldn't hold it against her.

07:23.960 --> 07:24.880
Jiang.

07:24.960 --> 07:27.280
If you have something to say, hurry up.

07:27.360 --> 07:28.520
Look,

07:28.600 --> 07:31.000
so many bad things happened before.

07:32.000 --> 07:33.240
Can you not hold it against me?

07:34.320 --> 07:36.880
Actually, I came here today
to make up for it.

07:36.960 --> 07:38.240
I'm introducing you to someone.

07:38.320 --> 07:39.400
Take a good look.

07:39.480 --> 07:41.680
Look, if you like this man…

07:44.720 --> 07:45.640
Stop right there!

07:45.720 --> 07:46.680
Stop right there!

07:46.760 --> 07:49.040
Look, the phone's screen cracked.

07:49.120 --> 07:50.960
- You need to pay for it!
- What's going on?

07:51.040 --> 07:51.760
- None of your business!
- Are you trying to scam her?

07:51.840 --> 07:53.200
- I'm talking to her!
- Who are you?

07:53.280 --> 07:54.480
Who am I? I'm her aunt!

07:54.560 --> 07:55.880
- Who are you?
- I…

07:55.960 --> 07:58.160
- Who are you? Speak up!
- I'm her boyfriend!

07:58.240 --> 07:59.560
Boyfriend, huh? Perfect timing!

08:02.680 --> 08:05.600
At such a young age,
you already learned to seduce men, huh?

08:05.680 --> 08:07.080
Isn't that shameless?

08:09.480 --> 08:11.760
Acting all mysterious
in the middle of the night.

08:11.840 --> 08:13.560
Do you want to scare our whole family?

08:13.640 --> 08:15.560
Didn't I feed you enough during the day?

08:15.640 --> 08:16.680
- Miss.
- What are you trying to do?

08:16.760 --> 08:18.560
Don't touch me!

08:18.640 --> 08:20.040
I can walk by myself! Don't touch me!

08:20.120 --> 08:21.920
Fine. You all just wait!

08:22.000 --> 08:23.200
Wait!

08:23.280 --> 08:24.320
Don't touch me!

08:24.400 --> 08:25.400
I'm telling you, this matter's not over!

08:25.480 --> 08:26.560
Just wait, you all!

08:29.160 --> 08:30.520
Crazy.

08:31.840 --> 08:33.159
Are you alright, Yifan?

08:34.520 --> 08:35.559
Yifan.

08:37.919 --> 08:39.799
See, how despicable she is!

08:40.320 --> 08:42.440
Look at you, playing the hero
and saving the beauty!

08:42.520 --> 08:45.680
I'm the only gentleman
in our combo, after all.

08:45.760 --> 08:46.640
Not necessarily.

08:46.720 --> 08:48.360
I heard they're recruiting new people.

08:49.360 --> 08:50.560
So what?

08:57.840 --> 08:59.840
Yifan, here, your breakfast.

09:00.360 --> 09:02.560
You must eat. Your health comes first.

09:03.080 --> 09:04.040
Thanks.

09:05.000 --> 09:07.160
Fu Zhuang, go with me
for this morning's outdoor interview.

09:07.240 --> 09:08.080
Let's go.

09:08.160 --> 09:09.920
Outdoor interview? Is there one today?

09:10.000 --> 09:11.760
Yes. Let's go!

09:11.840 --> 09:13.560
Honestly. Let's go!

09:14.080 --> 09:15.360
Don't forget to eat breakfast.

09:57.080 --> 09:58.160
She's at home.

09:59.720 --> 10:02.080
What's she doing?
Why isn't she coming out all night?

10:21.040 --> 10:22.840
I'm here. Are you ignoring me?

10:29.120 --> 10:30.360
Can't you sleep again?

10:32.680 --> 10:33.640
Walking around like this
in the middle of the night,

10:33.720 --> 10:34.880
it's quite scary.

10:35.640 --> 10:36.960
Do you want me to turn on the light?

10:43.280 --> 10:44.280
Wen Yifan.

10:57.840 --> 10:58.760
If you're feeling down,

10:58.840 --> 11:02.520
I can I can tough it out
and chat with you.

11:19.960 --> 11:21.160
What's wrong?

11:32.840 --> 11:34.120
Say something.

11:53.600 --> 11:55.320
Wen Yifan. Hey…

12:18.960 --> 12:20.080
What's going on?

12:35.480 --> 12:36.840
I haven't changed my clothes?

12:43.640 --> 12:44.680
Morning.

12:46.000 --> 12:47.480
What time did you get back last night?

12:49.560 --> 12:50.600
You don't know?

12:51.240 --> 12:52.840
I went to sleep early last night,

12:52.920 --> 12:54.760
so I didn't know when you came back.

13:00.480 --> 13:01.800
I have an appointment. I'll go now.

13:17.320 --> 13:18.720
Finally, you're on vacation.

13:18.800 --> 13:20.880
I've been dying
for these noodles for ages.

13:20.960 --> 13:22.880
I think it's not that great.

13:22.960 --> 13:24.120
Don't you think it's a bit too bland?

13:24.880 --> 13:26.440
It's alright.

13:27.760 --> 13:30.480
- I can make these noodles for you anytime.
- Are the buns good?

13:30.560 --> 13:32.520
- They're good.
- Hey, you kid.

13:32.600 --> 13:33.680
Come here.

13:33.760 --> 13:34.800
The kid doesn't know better.

13:34.880 --> 13:36.680
Sorry to bother you. Come.

13:36.760 --> 13:38.360
- Dad's here.
- Come. Sit down.

13:39.000 --> 13:39.840
Come.

13:39.920 --> 13:41.680
Cui Jingyu?

13:45.880 --> 13:46.840
Zhong Siqiao!

13:49.720 --> 13:50.960
Long time no see!

13:51.040 --> 13:51.880
How have you been?

13:52.640 --> 13:53.720
Pretty good.

13:53.800 --> 13:55.640
You came with a friend to have noodles?

13:57.760 --> 14:01.400
Aren't you Wen Yifan from Class 17?

14:02.280 --> 14:03.320
Yes.

14:03.400 --> 14:06.400
We didn't see you
at the last class reunion.

14:06.480 --> 14:07.920
I came back to Nanwu not long ago.

14:08.000 --> 14:09.560
Oh.

14:09.640 --> 14:11.720
So, how did it go with him?

14:11.800 --> 14:13.680
- Who?
- Sang Yan.

14:13.760 --> 14:17.160
I saw him that day
during the opening of Overtime.

14:21.640 --> 14:22.920
How have you been recently?

14:23.720 --> 14:27.040
I'm different from you
career-driven women.

14:27.120 --> 14:30.240
I can only revolve around my husband
and my kid.

14:33.520 --> 14:36.400
After all these years,
you've changed quite a bit.

14:38.760 --> 14:41.200
How about I introduce my husband to you?

14:41.280 --> 14:42.440
Hubby, come here.

14:45.720 --> 14:46.720
This is my husband.

14:46.800 --> 14:48.720
We recently started a small company.

14:48.800 --> 14:50.640
We plan to go public next year.

14:52.640 --> 14:54.120
Are you still single?

14:54.200 --> 14:55.760
I can have my husband

14:55.840 --> 14:57.800
Introduce some
of his rich bachelor friends

14:57.880 --> 14:59.440
- to both of you.
- No need, thanks.

15:01.440 --> 15:02.320
Yan!

15:02.920 --> 15:04.120
- You kid!
- What are you doing?

15:04.200 --> 15:05.760
- Yan?
- Come here.

15:05.840 --> 15:08.000
- Which "Yan"?
- "Yan" from "Yan'an".

15:11.640 --> 15:13.400
- Continue eating?
- Let's leave.

15:18.760 --> 15:20.840
We're done eating. We'll leave first.

15:21.360 --> 15:22.960
Okay. We'll make plans next time.

15:23.040 --> 15:24.000
Okay, bye.

15:31.440 --> 15:32.840
Yan!

15:32.920 --> 15:35.080
I didn't expect her to be so obsessed.

15:35.160 --> 15:36.040
Is it really necessary?

15:36.120 --> 15:37.360
Of course it is!

15:37.440 --> 15:40.000
When she was in school,
she kept talking about Sang Yan every day.

15:40.080 --> 15:41.680
Some people in our class
didn't know about Sang Yan,

15:41.760 --> 15:43.320
but because of her, they all found out.

15:51.840 --> 15:53.680
No. No.

15:53.760 --> 15:56.200
Sang Yan, Jing is looking for you.

16:03.360 --> 16:06.200
Sang Yan, I heard from someone

16:07.120 --> 16:09.160
that you're chasing
the dance student from your class.

16:10.400 --> 16:12.640
Is that why you're ignoring me?

16:13.960 --> 16:14.800
What does it have to do with you?

16:14.880 --> 16:16.880
I'm just curious.

16:22.400 --> 16:24.120
If that's not the case,

16:26.560 --> 16:27.920
I want to tell you something.

16:28.000 --> 16:29.440
Actually, I really like you--

16:29.520 --> 16:31.240
Does the school allow early romance now?

16:35.920 --> 16:38.840
Then we can agree
to wait until university.

16:43.640 --> 16:45.320
As for the rumor about you and Wen Yifan,

16:46.360 --> 16:48.120
I simply heard it from others.

16:48.200 --> 16:49.760
You don't need to be upset about it.

16:50.600 --> 16:53.280
This rumor has been spread so many times.

16:53.800 --> 16:54.640
They're really boring.

16:55.240 --> 16:57.560
I knew it. It's definitely all fake!

16:58.560 --> 17:00.760
I just mentioned it casually.

17:01.520 --> 17:02.960
Have I denied it?

17:09.079 --> 17:10.280
Also,

17:11.119 --> 17:13.640
I don't like your type.

17:15.119 --> 17:17.680
I'm passionate and lively.
You don't like me?

17:18.480 --> 17:20.160
I call it pestering.

17:35.680 --> 17:37.680
I saw my aunt again yesterday.

17:38.400 --> 17:41.400
Back then, weren't you unhappy
staying at her place?

17:44.520 --> 17:47.200
When I first moved to my uncle's house,

17:47.280 --> 17:50.800
my aunt said something one night.

17:51.480 --> 17:52.680
What did she say?

17:52.760 --> 17:54.400
At that time, my cousin was in college.

17:55.200 --> 17:57.400
He'd only come back every once in a while.

17:58.400 --> 18:01.480
Every time he came back,
my aunt would buy him chicken soup

18:02.120 --> 18:03.440
to nourish him.

18:06.560 --> 18:07.880
Then, one time,

18:07.960 --> 18:10.880
I was called in
because of an early romance.

18:12.000 --> 18:13.480
My aunt scolded me.

18:14.520 --> 18:16.800
After I got home, in front of me,

18:16.880 --> 18:18.080
she told my cousin…

18:18.160 --> 18:20.240
This is the expensive
chicken soup I bought.

18:20.320 --> 18:21.840
You have to drink it all
to nourish yourself.

18:21.920 --> 18:24.000
I don't want that.
How can I finish all of it?

18:24.080 --> 18:25.600
Jiang, drink it.

18:25.680 --> 18:27.080
Why should she get
to drink such good stuff?

18:27.160 --> 18:28.720
She doesn't deserve it!

18:29.800 --> 18:32.240
But I didn't take it too seriously.

18:32.320 --> 18:34.560
I just considered it a stranger's comment.

18:34.640 --> 18:37.440
But gradually, I actually started
taking that comment to heart.

18:38.880 --> 18:41.040
Because at the time, I was someone…

18:42.280 --> 18:43.680
Jiang, I really hate to scold you,

18:43.760 --> 18:45.480
but look at you.

18:45.560 --> 18:46.840
Instead of focusing on study,

18:47.600 --> 18:49.920
you're starting relationships!

18:50.000 --> 18:51.040
You know what?

18:51.120 --> 18:53.160
You've completely embarrassed me!

18:53.240 --> 18:55.760
- Enough.
- Enough?

18:55.840 --> 18:57.120
Looking at her just annoys me.

18:58.480 --> 18:59.520
Yifan,

18:59.600 --> 19:02.560
we really don't have
the energy to manage you.

19:03.560 --> 19:04.680
You need to behave.

19:04.760 --> 19:07.080
Don't do anything out of line.

19:07.160 --> 19:09.800
Otherwise, how will I face your late dad?

19:10.400 --> 19:11.920
I don't mean to blame you,

19:12.520 --> 19:14.200
but you need to understand.

19:14.280 --> 19:16.840
We're not obligated to support you.

19:16.920 --> 19:18.040
Right?

19:19.360 --> 19:20.720
Mom.

19:24.120 --> 19:26.680
Can you take me back home?

19:27.200 --> 19:28.440
I promise,

19:28.960 --> 19:31.080
I'll get along well with Zheng Kejia.

19:31.160 --> 19:33.000
I'll also get along well with Uncle Zheng.

19:34.840 --> 19:36.800
Can you take me back home?

19:36.880 --> 19:38.480
Jiang, stop crying.

19:38.560 --> 19:39.840
Listen.

19:40.360 --> 19:41.840
No matter what,

19:41.920 --> 19:43.920
you can't have
an early romance. Understand?

19:44.000 --> 19:45.360
I didn't!

19:45.440 --> 19:47.760
Mom, I'm back.

19:47.840 --> 19:50.000
Jiang, if there's anything,

19:50.080 --> 19:51.600
you can talk to your uncle.

19:51.680 --> 19:53.200
- I'll hang up now.
- Mom…

19:56.920 --> 19:58.160
I realized

19:58.840 --> 20:01.720
I was a burden
that everyone would try to avoid.

20:03.280 --> 20:05.480
There really was no need
to give me such good things.

20:06.960 --> 20:09.880
Dian, you don't need to mind those words.

20:14.480 --> 20:17.120
I still don't think
that statement was very accurate.

20:17.880 --> 20:20.920
But when I see those hundred-yuan skirts

20:21.440 --> 20:23.240
or those cheap little cakes,

20:24.000 --> 20:25.200
I still hesitate for a long time.

20:25.280 --> 20:26.920
I can't bring myself
to buy them for myself.

20:29.600 --> 20:31.000
It's not that I can't afford them.

20:32.960 --> 20:36.040
It's just that those expensive things

20:36.120 --> 20:38.360
really feel like a waste when used on me.

20:39.160 --> 20:40.160
What about Sang Yan?

20:40.960 --> 20:42.920
Are you sure he doesn't like you?

20:44.560 --> 20:46.400
Don't you think it's a bit strange?

20:46.480 --> 20:49.520
With his personality,
and he's not lacking money,

20:49.600 --> 20:51.200
why would he even consider
sharing a place with someone?

20:53.920 --> 20:55.160
I'm pretty sure.

20:56.200 --> 20:57.720
Because I've been really bad to him.

21:11.000 --> 21:12.000
Did you get home?

21:13.240 --> 21:16.480
I didn't expect the teacher
would call in the parents

21:16.560 --> 21:17.960
because of this.

21:18.480 --> 21:19.320
It's my fault. I affected you.

21:19.400 --> 21:20.400
I'm sorry.

21:22.760 --> 21:24.920
- Have your family…
- Sang Yan.

21:29.560 --> 21:31.680
Could you stop bothering me in the future?

21:36.240 --> 21:37.360
There was a time

21:37.440 --> 21:39.440
when I was very sharp-tempered.

21:39.520 --> 21:40.880
Sang Yan was the only one

21:41.960 --> 21:43.320
who treated me well.

21:44.880 --> 21:46.560
But I hurt him.

21:47.880 --> 21:49.320
With your temper,

21:49.400 --> 21:51.360
are you sure you can hurt him?

21:51.880 --> 21:53.600
Maybe you're overthinking it.

21:54.440 --> 21:56.920
For him, it might not be such a big deal.

21:57.000 --> 22:00.840
If you apologize and explain,
it will be fine.

22:01.640 --> 22:03.680
Forget it. It's been so long.

22:03.760 --> 22:06.760
Apologizing is never too late.

22:06.840 --> 22:08.360
Your mouth is on your own body.

22:08.440 --> 22:10.200
You can say whatever you want.

22:10.280 --> 22:11.160
It's your right.

22:11.240 --> 22:15.040
Whether the other part accepts it,
that's their right.

22:33.120 --> 22:34.320
I'm back.

22:53.640 --> 22:55.640
Apologizing is never too late.

22:56.400 --> 22:57.840
Your mouth is on your own body.

22:57.920 --> 22:59.640
You can say whatever you want.

22:59.720 --> 23:01.080
It's your right.

23:03.400 --> 23:07.040
Did you check on the progress
of your house renovation?

23:10.080 --> 23:11.040
How's it going?

23:11.120 --> 23:12.240
The house isn't finished yet.

23:12.320 --> 23:15.080
Even if it's finished,
it still needs to air out.

23:15.880 --> 23:18.360
It'll probably take longer
before I can move in.

23:21.440 --> 23:23.480
So, you won't move in a month later?

23:23.560 --> 23:24.800
That's the plan.

23:27.880 --> 23:29.240
You don't need to be so happy about it.

23:38.440 --> 23:40.160
What's up with that woman?

23:41.680 --> 23:43.240
Probably hungry.

23:44.000 --> 23:46.720
By the way, there's some extra
chicken soup I made on the table.

23:46.800 --> 23:47.640
Can you help me drink some?

24:02.240 --> 24:03.400
What's up with that woman?

24:06.240 --> 24:07.920
You think I'm scared of you?

24:09.200 --> 24:10.520
You think I'm scared of you?

24:11.120 --> 24:13.280
Maybe it's a case of dual personality.

24:15.040 --> 24:17.160
But to me, it looks
more like sleepwalking.

24:27.160 --> 24:29.400
Maybe I don't fully understand,

24:29.480 --> 24:30.920
but dual personality

24:31.000 --> 24:33.640
is when a person
suddenly develops another personality.

24:34.280 --> 24:37.040
Sometimes it feels like they're possessed,

24:37.560 --> 24:39.800
acting in ways
that are different from usual.

24:39.880 --> 24:42.240
Even their expressions
and behavior change.

24:42.320 --> 24:43.600
But sleepwalking is different.

24:48.200 --> 24:51.880
Sleepwalking happens during deep sleep.

24:51.960 --> 24:55.080
They perform meaningless actions
in familiar surroundings.

24:59.960 --> 25:01.840
How do you know so much?

25:07.560 --> 25:09.960
Because… I used to sleepwalk.

25:24.080 --> 25:27.920
Actually, I only started sleepwalking
after my dad passed away.

25:29.480 --> 25:31.400
It also happened at my uncle's house.

25:31.480 --> 25:32.800
I scared them.

25:33.760 --> 25:35.960
It happened in my college dorm too.

25:36.040 --> 25:37.560
But I stopped sleepwalking after that.

25:41.280 --> 25:44.560
How do you know
you haven't sleepwalked again since then?

25:44.640 --> 25:46.880
Because no one
has ever mentioned it to me again.

25:50.800 --> 25:52.880
Your roommate after that
didn't bring it up?

25:55.280 --> 25:57.280
I've rented with Lin for a short time.

25:57.880 --> 26:00.720
Before that, at Urban Haven,
no one ever mentioned it to me.

26:01.680 --> 26:03.960
Only after I came back to Nanwu
that I started sharing a place.

26:04.040 --> 26:05.920
I never had such
an experience before that.

26:13.080 --> 26:15.000
Did I sleepwalk in front of you?

26:19.960 --> 26:21.040
Did I?

26:29.640 --> 26:32.560
So, after you came back last night,

26:32.640 --> 26:34.360
you saw me sleepwalking?

26:39.520 --> 26:40.840
Did I do anything?

26:46.480 --> 26:48.800
You were just sitting here,

26:48.880 --> 26:50.320
head down, not saying a word,

26:50.400 --> 26:52.440
then constantly
fiddling with your sleeves.

26:53.240 --> 26:54.320
Then,

26:56.200 --> 26:57.480
you went back to your room.

27:03.200 --> 27:05.160
- Sorry, I scared you.
- Wen Yifan,

27:05.880 --> 27:07.640
I'm a grown man.
What could you possibly scare me with?

27:07.720 --> 27:10.320
Besides, I'm not scared of anything.

27:10.400 --> 27:11.800
That's good.

27:16.520 --> 27:18.080
Actually,

27:18.160 --> 27:20.520
when I used to sleepwalk
in my college dorm,

27:20.600 --> 27:23.080
I once scared a classmate
who got up to use the bathroom.

27:23.160 --> 27:25.760
After those nights,
I didn't dare to sleep much.

27:25.840 --> 27:27.040
I was afraid I'd scare others again.

27:28.160 --> 27:29.560
But she told me,

27:29.640 --> 27:32.000
when I sleepwalk, I don't do anything.

27:32.080 --> 27:33.200
Don't worry.

27:35.520 --> 27:38.960
If it happens again,
just pretend I'm invisible.

27:45.640 --> 27:48.200
Actually, as long as I sleep well,
I won't sleepwalk.

27:49.120 --> 27:51.200
It won't affect you either.

27:58.880 --> 28:01.320
I think it's the first time
I've sleepwalked in front of you.

28:01.400 --> 28:03.760
- Of course… No.
- Is there another time?

28:03.840 --> 28:05.720
- There's one more.
- What happened that time?

28:05.800 --> 28:08.240
Let me think. Ah, I remember now!

28:08.920 --> 28:09.800
What happened?

28:17.760 --> 28:19.120
You suddenly ran over,

28:20.040 --> 28:21.040
hugged me,

28:22.200 --> 28:23.400
and even…

28:26.240 --> 28:27.120
kissed me on the cheek.

28:34.960 --> 28:36.320
Why's your face turning red?

28:36.400 --> 28:38.160
Are you feeling unwell? Is your head hot?

28:38.240 --> 28:39.120
Are you alright?

28:39.200 --> 28:40.080
- Did it happen?
- Are you sick?

28:41.800 --> 28:43.200
No. Maybe the soup was too hot.

28:44.000 --> 28:45.800
The soup was too hot? Oh, I see.

28:45.880 --> 28:48.120
That's true. Who wouldn't blush
after drinking hot soup?

28:53.840 --> 28:56.160
Is this story exaggerated by you?

28:56.240 --> 28:57.800
Is it possible
that when I was sleepwalking,

28:57.880 --> 29:00.000
I accidentally bumped into you
and there was simply some body contact?

29:00.880 --> 29:02.160
Are you implying
that I deliberately slandered you?

29:02.240 --> 29:03.640
- That's not what I mean.
- Wen Yifan,

29:03.720 --> 29:05.520
I'm the one who got taken advantage of.

29:05.600 --> 29:07.120
How can you turn this around?

29:11.040 --> 29:13.240
If that had happened,
why didn't you tell me later?

29:13.320 --> 29:14.280
Didn't I?

29:20.160 --> 29:21.680
What's the thumbs-up for?

29:24.680 --> 29:26.160
An early morning encouragement?

29:27.360 --> 29:28.200
Sorry.

29:28.280 --> 29:30.480
It's okay. You explained it.
It's a special time.

29:30.560 --> 29:31.560
I'm not a petty person.

29:32.240 --> 29:33.240
But what does this mean?

29:33.320 --> 29:36.560
Well, what you think about
during the day will reflect in…

29:37.600 --> 29:38.920
sleepwalking.

29:39.840 --> 29:40.920
Sorry.

29:45.080 --> 29:46.080
Can I ask you a question?

29:46.160 --> 29:47.800
- Go ahead.
- Where did I kiss you?

29:54.880 --> 29:57.640
That spot? With our height difference,

29:58.400 --> 29:59.480
I can't reach it.

30:11.320 --> 30:12.600
It's okay.

30:12.680 --> 30:14.120
It's okay. You don't have to admit it.

30:14.200 --> 30:15.440
I forgive you.

30:16.080 --> 30:17.120
Hey…

30:27.800 --> 30:30.080
Then how about we reenact the scene?

30:32.040 --> 30:33.640
You want to take advantage of me again?

30:34.600 --> 30:36.400
Can you stand up for a while?

30:39.560 --> 30:41.400
Don't worry. I won't touch you.

30:41.480 --> 30:43.280
I just want to confirm something.

30:43.360 --> 30:45.400
I think the possibility
of this happening is a bit low.

31:09.280 --> 31:10.600
I definitely can't reach it.

31:15.440 --> 31:17.320
Maybe there's some misunderstanding?

31:18.280 --> 31:19.680
Or did I tiptoe?

31:21.480 --> 31:22.560
Or maybe you…

31:23.480 --> 31:24.640
lowered your head?

31:54.120 --> 31:55.440
Well, um…

31:58.880 --> 32:00.680
I'm just guessing here.

32:00.760 --> 32:02.160
You really have no reason to lie to me.

32:03.200 --> 32:05.600
But these actions
are really not something I can control.

32:05.680 --> 32:07.560
If this happens again,

32:07.640 --> 32:08.640
just punch me.

32:09.400 --> 32:11.600
Punch you? Can you handle that?

32:13.920 --> 32:15.400
Well, just handle the case properly.

32:15.480 --> 32:17.680
No, I mean,

32:17.760 --> 32:19.240
just make sure you protect yourself.

32:25.160 --> 32:27.080
How embarrassing.

32:59.960 --> 33:01.440
SLEEPWALK

33:06.880 --> 33:11.200
IT MAINLY HAPPENS
IN THE FIRST HALF OF THE NIGHT

33:11.280 --> 33:13.440
"The causes include stress from life,

33:14.040 --> 33:15.400
emotional suppression,

33:17.400 --> 33:19.480
post-traumatic stress disorder,

33:20.680 --> 33:21.960
panic disorder,

33:22.680 --> 33:25.800
or perhaps it's a mental scar
after being hurt."

33:29.960 --> 33:32.480
APRIL 4TH, QINGMING FESTIVAL

33:57.360 --> 33:58.400
It's fine.

33:58.920 --> 34:00.840
Nothing should've happened last night.

34:26.280 --> 34:30.199
TOMB OF LOVING FATHER WEN LIANGZHE

34:30.280 --> 34:32.880
Dad, I came to visit you.

34:33.920 --> 34:36.800
I brought you your favorite
spicy chicken soup.

34:37.400 --> 34:38.480
I'll serve it to you now.

34:48.440 --> 34:49.880
Still the same taste.

34:50.400 --> 34:52.320
If you ever want more,

34:53.239 --> 34:54.520
just tell me in my dream.

34:59.200 --> 35:00.120
Dad,

35:01.680 --> 35:05.400
are you lonely being alone?

35:08.640 --> 35:09.800
Now,

35:11.680 --> 35:13.400
I'm doing pretty well.

35:14.000 --> 35:15.960
But I kind of miss you.

35:17.320 --> 35:18.920
Mom is doing well too.

35:24.440 --> 35:27.080
Uncle Zheng has also been good to me.

35:29.520 --> 35:30.840
Dad, don't worry,

35:32.080 --> 35:35.560
I will take care of myself.

35:44.320 --> 35:45.720
NANWU TRIO - 3 MEMBERS
XIANG LANG'S MESSAGE

35:45.800 --> 35:47.320
Goodbye, Dian.

35:47.400 --> 35:48.600
Goodbye, Qiao.

35:48.680 --> 35:49.680
QIAO, ABOUT THE BRACELET
I DIDN'T EXPLAIN IT CLEARLY. I'M SORRY

35:49.760 --> 35:51.080
I hope the next time we meet,

35:51.600 --> 35:53.880
we can be like
the original Nanwu Trio again.

35:53.960 --> 35:54.800
I'M LEAVING NANWU

35:54.880 --> 35:55.800
I'VE APPLIED TO TRANSFER
TO THE HONG KONG BRANCH WITH THE COMPANY

35:55.880 --> 35:56.720
IT'S A RARE OPPORTUNITY
ACTUALLY, DIAN WAS RIGHT

35:56.800 --> 35:58.000
ALL ALONG, I'VE ONLY FOCUSED ON MYSELF
I NEVER TRULY UNDERSTOOD YOU GUYS

36:05.560 --> 36:07.880
Here we go! I'm getting faster!

36:07.960 --> 36:09.240
Sit tight.

36:10.160 --> 36:12.400
Shuangjiang, hug me tight.

36:14.280 --> 36:15.160
Is it thrilling?

36:15.240 --> 36:16.600
Thrilling!

36:16.680 --> 36:18.920
I'm getting faster again!
I'm getting faster again!

36:19.000 --> 36:20.000
Hug me tight!

36:20.080 --> 36:21.080
Hug me tight…

36:43.760 --> 36:45.280
It's already past ten.

36:45.360 --> 36:47.200
You didn't even send a message.

36:47.280 --> 36:49.400
Where have you been?

36:53.400 --> 36:54.800
Haven't you eaten yet?

36:55.880 --> 36:56.840
Not yet.

37:01.920 --> 37:03.680
I bought some chicken soup.

37:04.560 --> 37:05.400
Try it.

37:19.160 --> 37:20.280
The chicken soup

37:21.440 --> 37:22.520
is specially for you.

38:03.320 --> 38:04.400
Thank you.

38:53.640 --> 38:56.400
As expected, it's starting again.

40:03.000 --> 40:04.400
Finally saw me?

40:07.000 --> 40:08.120
What are you thinking about?

40:34.320 --> 40:35.240
What's wrong?

41:32.160 --> 41:33.160
Wen Shuangjiang,

41:35.480 --> 41:36.760
you kissed me just now.

41:39.480 --> 41:40.480
I didn't lie to you this time.

41:45.360 --> 41:47.080
Why did you kiss me and just leave?

41:55.360 --> 41:57.600
I can't stand being taken advantage of.

41:58.520 --> 41:59.960
This time, you owe me.

42:16.920 --> 42:18.280
After you wake up,

42:20.080 --> 42:21.200
return it to me.

42:41.840 --> 42:44.680
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

42:50.440 --> 42:52.040
She has already come.

43:06.360 --> 43:11.080
TOMB OF LOVING FATHER WEN LIANGZHE

43:13.480 --> 43:14.440
Uncle,

43:16.480 --> 43:17.920
I met your daughter again.

43:25.960 --> 43:26.880
These years,

43:29.800 --> 43:31.080
has she been happy?

46:16.760 --> 46:18.000
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

46:18.080 --> 46:19.040
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
